examples/mud_2D/sqexp_cartesian_10_10_rho_0_sample_9/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_10_10_rho_0_sample_9.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_10_10_rho_0_sample_9.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_5/run11/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_200/run2/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]

  [../]

  [../]

    block = 'film'

    block = 'substrate'

  [./strain]

    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]

    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_200/run5/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.548134E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.548134E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 8.333333E+02
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.548134E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.548134E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_3/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_exp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_3.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_3.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_10/run3/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_5/run1/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp

  [../]

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]

examples/mud_2D/sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_1/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_1.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_1.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]

  [../]

    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]

    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]

    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_10/run1/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '2.511886E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '2.511886E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.812010E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.812010E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 2.511886E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 2.511886E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./fracture_energy]
    type = FractureEnergy
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  dt = 6.992472E-06

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load fracture_energy'
  exodus = true
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

  [../]

    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]

    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_1/run13/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]

      secondary = 'right'

      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]

  [../]

  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false

    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_10/run4/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '5.011872E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '5.011872E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]

    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress

    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.812010E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.812010E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]

  [../]

      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_5/run9/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '1.584893E+01 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '1.584893E+01 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 2.083333E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.503124E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.503124E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 1.584893E-01
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 1.584893E-01
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./fracture_energy]
    type = FractureEnergy
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  dt = 4.788671E-06

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load fracture_energy'
  exodus = true
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

  [../]
[]

  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'

[Variables]

  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_2D/sqexp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_1/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_1.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_sample_1.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_0.5/run3/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.981072E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.981072E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 2.083333E+00
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.055164E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.055164E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.981072E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.981072E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./fracture_energy]
    type = FractureEnergy
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  dt = 5.837227E-06

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load fracture_energy'
  exodus = true
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

examples/mud_2D_qualitative/exp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_seed_g/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_exp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_seed_g.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_25_rho_0_seed_g.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

  [../]

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_0.5/run8/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]

    block = 'substrate'

    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]

examples/mud_3D/L_7/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = '../gold/psic_L_7_rho_0_sample_1.txt'
  [../]

    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = '../gold/Gc_L_7_rho_0_sample_1.txt'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./disp_z]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_z]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_z
    component = 2
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./x_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
  [./y_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
  [./z_fix]
    type = PresetBC
    variable = disp_z
    value = 0
    boundary = 'bottom'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    initial_stress_zz = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y disp_z'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]

  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      preonly       ilu          200         200                0                    '
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -ksp_grmres_restart -sub_ksp_type -sub_pc_type -pc_asm_overlap'
  # petsc_options_value = 'asm      31                  preonly       ilu          2'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -mat_mffd_err -pc_factor_shift_type -pc_factor_shift_amount'
  # petsc_options_value = 'ilu      1e-5          NONZERO               1e-15'
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_10/run13/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]

[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

      secondary = 'right'

    [../]

      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'

    [../]

    [../]

    value = 0

    initial_stress_yy = load

  [../]

    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]

    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

  [../]

  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp

    variable = 'd'

    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit

    block = 'film'
  [../]

    prop_values = '4.048456E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]

  [../]

    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_5/run12/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_9/mechanical.i

[Functions]

    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_9.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_9.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_10/run9/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

  [./disp_x]
  [../]

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_20/run13/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

      variable = disp_x

      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]

    type = LorentzDegradation

  [../]

  solve_type = 'NEWTON'

  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]

      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]

      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]

      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]

      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]

    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]

    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]

    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]

    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

    d = d
  [../]

    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
